missionEventData.data1: We have traced the arms used in the recent attack to a Mugaari cargo loading area in the Tungra Sector. We suspect that the Mugaari are providing arms and other aid to the Rebels. Our attack on this cargo area is timed to catch the Mugaari and Rebels in their next illicit weapons exchange. With the aide of the Fogger your mission objective is to destroy all cargo-carrying vessels at this site. Destroy everything, take no prisoners.
The enemy is already beginning to move. Switch to torpedos and fire at will!
Well done! All Mugaari freighters have been destroyed.
Excellent! All Rebel transports have been destroyed.
All enemy shuttles have been destroyed.
There are still rebel ships active. Take them out.
Well done. Return to the Fogger at once. We're moving out immediately!

missionEventData.data2: The Empire has been dealt a serious blow! The Emperor's secret weapon, the Death Star, has been destroyed. But justice has been swift. Darth Vader, the Emperor's special envoy, crushed the Rebel base on Hoth and now has the Rebels on the run. High Command have issued a warning to all Imperial outposts, be alert for Rebel forces attempting to flee their base on Hoth. Meanwhile, far out on the Outer Rim, the Imperial Tie Fighter pilot, Maarek Steele, begins his patrol...

missionEventData.data1: AOF - M04 Outpost D-34 Has Fallen
missionEventData.data3: While our assault was carried out with Imperial speed and precision, the Rebel ships were too easily destroyed. We now know that the operation was a decoy used to draw the Fogger away from Outpost-D34
